1
00:00:03,403 --> 00:00:04,571
I'm going to the bathroom.

2
00:00:17,283 --> 00:00:18,852
The bathroom is right there.

3
00:00:19,619 --> 00:00:20,720
Mind your own business.

4
00:00:21,254 --> 00:00:22,614
If you're going to leave, just go.

5
00:00:26,793 --> 00:00:28,427
It's not like I'm never coming back.

6
00:00:28,428 --> 00:00:30,096
You should be happy for me.

7
00:00:31,164 --> 00:00:32,431
I know.

8
00:00:32,432 --> 00:00:34,133
But you said you didn't want to go.

9
00:00:34,134 --> 00:00:34,934
Why the sudden change?

10
00:00:34,935 --> 00:00:37,203
It's time, Youzhi.

11
00:00:39,139 --> 00:00:40,239
We've known each other so long,

12
00:00:40,240 --> 00:00:41,608
we're closer than family.

13
00:00:42,375 --> 00:00:43,775
But you have your own life to live.

14
00:00:45,512 --> 00:00:47,212
She's a great girl.

15
00:00:47,213 --> 00:00:48,882
You should focus more on her.

16
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:51,650
And...

17
00:00:52,085 --> 00:00:54,005
after graduation, do
what you really want to do.

18
00:00:54,654 --> 00:00:56,856
Look out for each other.

19
00:00:59,292 --> 00:01:01,226
The way you're talking...

20
00:01:01,227 --> 00:01:03,396
it's like you're never coming back.

21
00:01:19,045 --> 00:01:20,580
Keep this safe for me.

22
00:01:20,814 --> 00:01:22,148
I'll come back for it later.

23
00:01:48,007 --> 00:01:49,309
Look at you.

24
00:01:50,176 --> 00:01:52,078
This is why I didn't want to tell you.

25
00:01:52,912 --> 00:01:54,432
It was hard enough to make up my mind.

26
00:01:55,648 --> 00:01:56,316
If the time comes

27
00:01:56,317 --> 00:01:57,984
and you're crying, begging me not to go,

28
00:01:58,918 --> 00:01:59,918
what am I supposed to do?

29
00:02:01,154 --> 00:02:02,194
Don't come to the airport.

30
00:02:02,755 --> 00:02:04,491
I don't want to cry in front of everyone.

31
00:02:04,958 --> 00:02:07,373
Otherwise, everyone will think
I'm the one getting dumped.

32
00:02:12,465 --> 00:02:13,600
Take care.

33
00:02:15,602 --> 00:02:17,303
Let's both take good care of ourselves.
